data.description: Check out this stunning LIKE NEW 2021 Manufactured Home situated on a .29 acre lot in Mulberry FL! You will fall in love the second you enter this home. Features include a spacious 3/2 layout with a split floorplan. The upgraded kitchen with a large island and bar is truly a chef's dream! It features beautiful white shaker-style cabinets, granite-look countertops, and a deep farmhouse sink with a barndoor slider pantry! The master bedroom is spacious and has a Pinterest-worthy en-suite bathroom! Double vanities with a lower makeup vanity in the center, gorgeous walk in shower, and a huge soaking tub you're sure to enjoy after a long day of work. The guest bedrooms are spacious and each room has a large walk in closet with tons of storage space. Don't miss this opportunity to own a turn key nearly new modular home for a great price! Schedule your showing today!
